snippet.title: Star Wars Jedi: Fallen Order – Designing BD-1
snippet.description:
In STAR WARS, droids are more than just robots. They have personality and heart; they're full-blown characters. See how the team behind STAR WARS Jedi: Fallen Order used stellar sound design and animation to create a character with heart.

STAR WARS Jedi: Fallen Order is a third-person action-adventure game from Respawn Entertainment. Become a Jedi on Xbox One, Playstation 4, and PC on November 15, 2019.

Pre-order now to get the Bee-D1 skin: https://www.ea.com/games/starwars/jedi-fallen-order/pre-order.
